text: Westercelle is a suburb of the district town of Celle in Lower Saxony, Germany, that is 3 kilometres (1.9 miles) south of the town centre on the river Fuhse. == Sources == * Artur Müller-Davidi: Westercelle: Hinweise für die Erforschung der Geschichte des Dorfes. Celle, 1981 * Horst Bolle: Chronik des Dorfes Westercelle. Celle, 1951 ==References== == Other websites == * Celle town website Category:Celle Category:Settlements in Lower Saxony
title: Westercelle
